<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Purchase Order</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .company-detail {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .doc-badge {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #eff6ff;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .meta-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .meta-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
        }

        .meta-item .label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .meta-item .value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .parties-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .party-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .party-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .party-name {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .party-detail {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .items-table thead th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .items-table thead th:nth-child(n+3) {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table tbody td {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .items-table tbody td:nth-child(n+3) {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .items-table tbody td:first-child {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            width: 36px;
        }

        .totals-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .totals-table {
            width: 300px;
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .total-row.grand {
            background: #111827;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .delivery-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .delivery-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .delivery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .delivery-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 4px 0;
        }

        .delivery-item .label {
            color: #6b7280;
            min-width: 140px;
        }

        .delivery-item .value {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .terms-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .terms-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .terms-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .note-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .note-box strong {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .sig-block {}

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 6px;
            min-width: 200px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div>
            <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="company-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if companyPhone}}<div class="company-detail">Phone: {{companyPhone}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if companyEmail}}<div class="company-detail">Email: {{companyEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="doc-badge">
            <div class="doc-title">PURCHASE ORDER</div>
            <div class="status-badge">Open Order</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">PO Number</div>
            <div class="value">{{poNumber}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Date</div>
            <div class="value">{{poDate}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
            <div class="label">Delivery Date</div>
            <div class="value">{{deliveryDate}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties-grid">
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Buyer (Bill To)</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="party-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if gstNumber}}<div class="party-detail"><strong>GST:</strong> {{gstNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Vendor (Supplier)</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{vendorName}}</div>
            <div class="party-detail">{{{vendorAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if vendorGST}}<div class="party-detail"><strong>GST:</strong> {{vendorGST}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if vendorEmail}}<div class="party-detail">Email: {{vendorEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <table class="items-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>#</th>
                <th>Item Description</th>
                <th>Qty</th>
                <th>Unit Price</th>
                <th>Amount</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each items}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{@index}}</td>
                <td>{{this.description}}</td>
                <td style="text-align:right;">{{this.quantity}}</td>
                <td>₹{{this.rate}}</td>
                <td>₹{{this.amount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="totals-section">
        <div class="totals-table">
            <div class="total-row"><span>Subtotal</span><span>₹{{subtotal}}</span></div>
            {{#if taxAmount}}<div class="total-row"><span>GST</span><span>₹{{taxAmount}}</span></div>{{/if}}
            {{#if shippingCost}}<div class="total-row"><span>Shipping</span><span>₹{{shippingCost}}</span></div>{{/if}}
            <div class="total-row grand"><span>Total Order</span><span>₹{{totalAmount}}</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="delivery-section">
        <div class="delivery-title">Delivery & Shipping Details</div>
        <div class="delivery-grid">
            <div class="delivery-item"><span class="label">Delivery Address:</span><span class="value">{{#if
                    deliveryAddress}}{{{deliveryAddress}}}{{else}}{{{companyAddress}}}{{/if}}</span></div>
            <div class="delivery-item"><span class="label">Expected Delivery:</span><span
                    class="value">{{deliveryDate}}</span></div>
            <div class="delivery-item"><span class="label">Shipping Method:</span><span class="value">{{#if
                    shippingMethod}}{{shippingMethod}}{{else}}Standard Delivery{{/if}}</span></div>
            <div class="delivery-item"><span class="label">Payment Terms:</span><span class="value">{{#if
                    paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}Net 30 days{{/if}}</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
        <div class="terms-title">Terms & Conditions</div>
        <ol class="terms-list">
            <li>This Purchase Order is subject to the buyer's standard terms and conditions.</li>
            <li>Goods must conform to the specifications and quality standards as agreed.</li>
            <li>Delivery must be made by the specified delivery date. Late deliveries may be subject to penalties.</li>
            <li>The buyer reserves the right to reject goods that do not meet specifications.</li>
            <li>Invoice must reference this PO number for processing.</li>
            <li>Payment will be processed within {{#if paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} of receiving
                a valid invoice.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="note-box">
        <strong>Important:</strong> This Purchase Order constitutes an offer to purchase goods/services as described. It
        becomes a binding contract upon acceptance by the vendor. Please confirm acceptance within 48 hours.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-block">
            <div class="sig-label">Authorized by (Buyer)</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{#if approverName}}{{approverName}}{{else}}Procurement Manager{{/if}}</div>
                <div class="sig-role">{{companyName}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-block">
            <div class="sig-label">Accepted by (Vendor)</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{vendorName}}</div>
                <div class="sig-role">Date: ___________</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{companyName}} — Purchase Order</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>